                                    <field name="l10n_ec_electronic_logo" widget="image" />
                                    <div
                                        class="text-muted"
                                        attrs="{'invisible' : [('l10n_ec_electronic_logo','!=',False)]}"
                                    >
                                        Please use image with size 450x150 px aprox.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h2 name="conection">Connection</h2>
                        <div class="row mt16 o_settings_container">
                            <div id="conection" class="col-12 col-md-6 o_setting_box">
                                <div class="o_setting_left_pane">

                                </div>
                                <div class="o_setting_right_pane">
                                    <label for="l10n_ec_type_environment" string="Environment Type" class="col-md-5" />
                                    <field name="l10n_ec_type_environment" widget="radio" class="o_light_label" />
                                    <div class="text-muted">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>
                                                <b>Testing:</b>
                                                The documents have no tributary validity
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                <b>Production:</b>
                                                The documents have tributary validity
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 o_setting_box">
                                <div class="o_setting_left_pane">

                                </div>
                                <div class="o_setting_right_pane">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_max_intentos" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_max_intentos" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_cron_process" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_cron_process" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_ws_timeout" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_ws_timeout" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_request_sri_validation_cancel_doc" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_request_sri_validation_cancel_doc" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-muted">
                                        <p>Check the box if you want the system to consult the SRI if a document is
                                            canceled in order to cancel it in the system, if it is not checked,
                                            the system will not validate the SRI and proceed to cancel the document
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12 col-md-12 o_setting_box">
                                <div class="o_setting_left_pane">

                                </div>
                                <div class="o_setting_right_pane">
                                    <label
                                        for="l10n_ec_type_conection_sri"
                                        string="Connection type with SRI"
                                        class="col-3"
                                    />
                                    <field name="l10n_ec_type_conection_sri" widget="radio" class="o_light_label" />
                                    <div class="text-muted">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>
                                                <b>On-Line:</b>
                                                Documents are authorized on real time with SRI
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                <b>Off-Line:</b>
                                                Documents are authorized on max time of 24 hours with SRI
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="o_form_label col-12">Web Services URL</span>
                                    <div
                                        class="col-12 col-md-12"
                                        attrs="{'invisible' : [('l10n_ec_type_environment','!=','production')]}"
                                    >
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <label
                                                for="l10n_ec_ws_receipt_production"
                                                string="Reception of Documents"
                                                class="col-5 o_light_label"
                                            />
                                            <field name="l10n_ec_ws_receipt_production" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <label
                                                for="l10n_ec_ws_auth_production"
                                                string="Authorization of Documents"
                                                class="col-5 o_light_label"
                                            />
                                            <field name="l10n_ec_ws_auth_production" />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div
                                        class="col-12 col-md-12"
                                        attrs="{'invisible' : [('l10n_ec_type_environment','!=','test')]}"
                                    >
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <label
                                                for="l10n_ec_ws_receipt_test"
                                                string="Reception of Documents"
                                                class="col-5 o_light_label"
                                            />
                                            <field name="l10n_ec_ws_receipt_test" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <label
                                                for="l10n_ec_ws_auth_test"
                                                string="Authorization of Documents"
                                                class="col-5 o_light_label"
                                            />
                                            <field name="l10n_ec_ws_auth_test" />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h2 name="signer">Electronic Certificate File</h2>
                        <div class="row mt16 o_settings_container">
                            <div id="signer" class="col-12 col-md-6 o_setting_box">
                                <div class="o_setting_left_pane">

                                </div>
                                <div class="o_setting_right_pane">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_key_type_id" class="col-5" />
                                        <field
                                            name="l10n_ec_key_type_id"
                                            domain="[('state', '=', 'valid')]"
                                            options="{'no_quick_create': True}"
                                            class="o_light_label"
                                        />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h2 name="documents">Default Values</h2>
                        <div class="row mt16 o_settings_container">
                            <div id="sri_default_values" class="col-12 col-md-6 o_setting_box">
                                <div class="o_setting_left_pane">

                                </div>
                                <div class="o_setting_right_pane">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_sri_payment_id" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_sri_payment_id" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <label for="l10n_ec_type_supplier_authorization" class="col-5" />
                                        <field name="l10n_ec_type_supplier_authorization" widget="radio" />
                                        <div class="text-muted">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <b>Simple:</b>
                                                    You only must be enter Authorization number, validations are done
                                                    online with SRI
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <b>Complete:</b>
                                                    You must be enter all information need to create supplier
                                                    authorization, Validations are done local and online with SRI
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
